item.title: CVE-2019-3917|2024-09-16T16:14:15.165Z -- tenable -- alcatel%20lucent%20i-240w-q%20gpon%20ont
item.description: The Alcatel Lucent I-240W-Q GPON ONT using firmware version 3FE54567BOZJ19 allows a remote, unauthenticated attacker to enable telnetd on the router via a crafted HTTP request.
